title: Big Brother USA 9 Live Feeds - 03-19-08
description:

After the show it started to get good, then they did some lame luxory comp outside for hours which blocked the feeds. I guess 4 people get to see the movie 21. As it stands right now James/chelsia will be on the block.

Part 1 - 19 min
Before the eviction. Joes off of on Sheila.

Part 2 - 26 min
Right after the feeds came back. Tons of action/convos.

Part 3 - 36 min
More random action. Too much to talk about as I was all over the place.

Part 4 - 8 min
Adam just got his HOH. Nat comes up to break down the game and did one hell of a job on it.

Part 5 - 18 min
Ryan/Adam/Nat have a big pow-wow in the HOH. Good stuff.

Part 6 - 13 min
James comes up to beg for his safety. We learn that Adam will put up James/Chelsia for sure.

Part 7 - 8 min
Josh makes a deal with Adam.

Part 8 - 28 min
Tons of action after the noms are set with people scrambling.

Part 9 - 26 min
More reaction + after the feeds came back and they talk about Allison counting cards.
